{"tid":275392,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[DIY] - 有無人有興趣自己整個玩具?","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T04:16:23.000Z","uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45c4d818b464144e03fa1b9d11a2ad472134f6f9","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"要精美的玩具你可以上一頁了.<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n<br />\n細個時去診所, 見過一個靠地方吸力左右滾動的玩具.<br />\n現在大家好想要一個.<br />\n<br />\n草圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/816hkfbj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F816hkfbj&h=5f2e84ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/njr5p1t7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnjr5p1t7&h=61191f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料亞加力膠板, 5mm厚.<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個只係草圖, D邊邊, 支撐, 好多仲要修改.<br />\n<br />\n玩法:<br />\n - 放圓碟在左右兩邊, 原碟因地心吸力, 左右移動, 啱晒強迫症D毒X睇到佢停<br />\n<br />\n設計重點:<br />\n - 畫可能增力左右滾動的次數<br />\n   - 圓碟材料要夠重<br />\n   - 圓碟滾動切面要相對少<br />\n   - 滑道要平滑 (廢話)<br />\n<br />\n擔心:<br />\n - 亞加力膠板會變形 (可用8mm原板, 或薄一點金屬版, $.$)<br />\n - 腳架支撐不夠力 (可多幾隻腳, 但不美觀 : ( )<br />\n - 設計錯誤, 不知滑道的深度 (現在高低點差距1cm, 長58cm)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩意見/提點?"},{"pid":"b3a3ed4b2a35d3dbf6657bf5d900da506bd9271d","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要精美的玩具你可以上一頁了.<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n<br />\n細個時去診所, 見過一個靠地方吸力左右滾動的玩具.<br />\n現在大家好想要一個.<br />\n<br />\n草圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/816hkfbj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F816hkfbj&h=5f2e84ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/njr5p1t7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnjr5p1t7&h=61191f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料亞加力膠板, 5mm厚.<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個只係草圖, D邊邊, 支撐, 好多仲要修改.<br />\n<br />\n玩法:<br />\n - 放圓碟在左右兩邊, 原碟因地心吸力, 左右移動, 啱晒強迫症D毒X睇到佢停<br />\n<br />\n設計重點:<br />\n - 畫可能增力左右滾動的次數<br />\n   - 圓碟材料要夠重<br />\n   - 圓碟滾動切面要相對少<br />\n   - 滑道要平滑 (廢話)<br />\n<br />\n擔心:<br />\n - 亞加力膠板會變形 (可用8mm原板, 或薄一點金屬版, $.$)<br />\n - 腳架支撐不夠力 (可多幾隻腳, 但不美觀 : ( )<br />\n - 設計錯誤, 不知滑道的深度 (現在高低點差距1cm, 長58cm)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩意見/提點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心呀文盲."},{"pid":"800da7a134613498ef49504f3290164f44ed5920","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"大個呀, 唔係大家呀, 唔好老屈連登仔"},{"pid":"3308f39b31cd06126c0a7f7084105033005fdd14","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"畫=&gt;盡"},{"pid":"91fb2876d300bc5b1556de709d0b8aecab4dcbc1","tid":275392,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZuPGJ5QiQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqZuPGJ5QiQ8&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=36ab9410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZuPGJ5QiQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 參考下"},{"pid":"41e6ae8b0c5f040ee422fcf3e656c801a9a52a45","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZuPGJ5QiQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqZuPGJ5QiQ8&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=36ab9410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZuPGJ5QiQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 參考下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我想要的, 但係想再長一點, Orz.<br />\n等我研究一下, Orz"},{"pid":"1a7cddaf574f65f08bc2cf30c6e22dcb1cfa5f44","tid":275392,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:16:23.0